   The Hunt Is On
   For an Elegant Lady
   Who Inflicts Pain
   ---
   Crawling Across Phoenix Are
   Six Million Black Widows;
   Locals Torch or Sell Them
   ----
   By Curtis R. Simmons
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
08/14/91
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE A1
</SO>
