   Super Aspirin's Promise Exemplifies Value of Biotech
   ---
   A Breakthrough Offers Possibility of
   Saving Tens of Thousands of Lives
   ----
   By Michael Waldholz
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
02/24/92
</DATE>
<SO>
